<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM2.2.5">
<l>takumcīrt taṉṟaṉi mutali ṉuḷḷē</l>
<l>mikuntē vummep poruḷum paṭaikkat</l>
<l>takuṅkō lattā maraikkaṇṇa ṉemmāṉ</l>
<l>mikuñcō timēla raṟivār yavarē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Inside his sole base of befitting excellence</l>
<l>to create all the many gods and things</l>
<l>our lord Kṛṣṇa with befitting beautiful lotus eyes,</l>
<l>who are those who know [any] above [him] in ample splendour?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
